General.Name: Deutsche Grundstücksauktionen AG
General.Description: Deutsche Grundstücksauktionen AG provides real estate auction services in Germany. The company is involved in auctioning of third-party real estate and third-party rights equivalent to real estate on behalf of private, commercial, and public owners, as well as conducts auctions online. It also engages in the brokerage business. The company was formerly known as Berliner Grundstücksauktionen-Organisationsgesellschaft mbH & Co KG and changed its name to Deutsche Grundstücksauktionen AG in 1998. Deutsche Grundstücksauktionen AG was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Berlin, Germany.
